snippet.title: Karlie Gusé Review Cases AD will never let go !
snippet.description:

This phrase keeps reverberating around my head.
For a while now I have been trying to get my head around the challenge where corruption seems to blight cases.  I have a problem because often they are victims of an injustice – maybe from a person or by the system. 
 the anger and pain these cases produce we just cant let them go,#
